data.description: Private and Peaceful setting in the Town of Lucas on 2.340 acres. This custom built home with 3 bedrooms, 2 and a 1/2 bath home is half log siding on the exterior and the interior has side car siding with vaulted ceilings. hardwood floors, granite countertops, pantry, main floor laundry. Enjoy evenings by the full stone gas fireplace. The lower level is fully finished with a family room, 2 bedrooms, full bath and it is a walk out. There is a large front porch and cedar deck on the back which has been recently reinforced for your hot tub enjoyment. The garage is oversized 34x31 and is heated. A Navien boiler provides floor heat to the garage, basement, master bath and domestic hot water. High Speed Fiber Optic provided by 24/7 Telecom is up and running in the house. The roof is steel. Come take a look at this one of a kind property!
